\[1 + 2\left(2\sin \frac{90^\circ - 180^\circ/2015}{2}\right) + 3\left(2\sin \frac{90^\circ - 2 \cdot 180^\circ/2015}{2}\right) + \dots + 2015\left(2\sin \frac{90^\circ - 2014 \cdot 180^\circ/2015}{2}\right).\]We can write this as
